$ Registry: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\CTF\LangBar

{ ShowStatus

  The value of `ShowStatus` determines how the *language bar* is shown:
    • 0: Floating on desktop
    • 3: Hidden
    • 4: Docked in the taskbar

}
{ Misc

  Apprently, in order to monitor the changes made to the → Windows/registry[registry] with
  → Windows/tools/Sysinternals/Procmon[procmon], the → Windows/development/Portable-Executable/DLL/rundll32_exe[`rundell32.exe`] process name needs to be enabled.


}
